---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Nick Ruffin | Manager, Data Product Engineering">
  <div class="container">
    <Hero />

    <section class="leading-section">
      <div class="leading-content">
        <span class="section-tag reveal">CURRENTLY LEADING</span>
        <h3 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">A clinical data product running in production today</h3>
        <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 lead-copy">RedSail's pharmacy claims data monetization platform &mdash; the product I architected and now lead the team behind. Raw upstream data through Datavant tokenization to automated client delivery, in production today.</p>

        <div class="leading-grid reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="leading-card">
            <span class="leading-label">SCALE</span>
            <p class="leading-headline">$9M ARR &middot; 6B records &middot; 8+ enterprise clients</p>
            <p class="leading-detail">Pharma, life sciences, and real-world evidence buyers. Multi-tenant feed orchestration with per-client SLAs, schedules, and compliance constraints.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="leading-card">
            <span class="leading-label">PLATFORM</span>
            <p class="leading-headline">Snowflake &middot; AWS &middot; MWAA V3 &middot; Datavant</p>
            <p class="leading-detail">Led V1 to V3 migration on Airflow managed service. IAM trust policy reconciliation across executor ARNs. Terraform-managed Snowflake + AWS environments.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="leading-card">
            <span class="leading-label">RECENT WORK</span>
            <p class="leading-headline">V2 tokenization rebuild</p>
            <p class="leading-detail">Ground-up rewrite: parallel client chains, pre-hashed archive joins, tokenize safety fixes. Cut wall-clock against the 35-37 min baseline. <a href="/case-studies/v2-tokenization-rebuild">Read the case study &rarr;</a></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="results-section">
      <div class="results-content">
        <span class="section-tag reveal">TRACK RECORD</span>
        <h3 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Built and operating at scale</h3>
        <div class="results-grid reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <div class="result-item">
            <span class="result-number" data-counter="9" data-prefix="$" data-suffix="M+">$0</span>
            <span class="result-label">Annual revenue from the data monetization platform</span>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <span class="result-number" data-counter="6" data-suffix="B">0</span>
            <span class="result-label">Records de-identified, tokenized, delivered</span>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <span class="result-number" data-counter="8" data-suffix="+">0</span>
            <span class="result-label">Enterprise pharma &amp; RWE clients</span>
          </div>
          <div class="result-item">
            <span class="result-number" data-counter="50" data-suffix="+">0</span>
            <span class="result-label">Automated daily workflows on MWAA V3</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="leadership-section">
      <div class="leadership-content">
        <span class="section-tag reveal">LEADERSHIP</span>
        <h3 class="reveal reveal-delay-1">Operating as a tech leader for years</h3>
        <div class="leadership-grid">
          <div class="leadership-row reveal reveal-delay-1">
            <div class="leadership-when">
              <span class="role-time">2025 &mdash; Present</span>
              <span class="role-company">RedSail Technologies</span>
            </div>
            <div class="leadership-what">
              <h4>Manager, Data Product Engineering</h4>
              <p>Lead the team behind RedSail's $9M ARR data monetization platform &mdash; the product I architected and built. MWAA V3 migration, V2 tokenization rebuild, multi-client backfill engineering, day-to-day delivery to enterprise buyers.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="leadership-row reveal reveal-delay-2">
            <div class="leadership-when">
              <span class="role-time">2021 &mdash; 2025</span>
              <span class="role-company">Nimble Solutions</span>
            </div>
            <div class="leadership-what">
              <h4>Director of Full Stack Development</h4>
              <p>Led three separate engineering teams across the US and Hyderabad as Director. Owned tech due diligence for 4 acquisitions. Traveled to India to integrate an acquired team. Delivered enterprise systems that transformed business operations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="leadership-cta reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <a href="/experience" class="text-cta">Full track record &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="cta-content reveal">
        <span class="cta-tag">LET'S TALK</span>
        <h3>Open to the right opportunity in healthcare data.</h3>
        <p>If you're hiring someone to build and scale a clinical data product, own delivery to enterprise buyers, and lead the team that runs it &mdash; I'd like to hear from you.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/nicholas-ruffin-a9b767102" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-button">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
          <a href="mailto:nruffinsecure@gmail.com" class="cta-button-secondary">Email directly</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .container { width: 100%; position: relative; overflow-x: hidden; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .leading-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--background-color);
    padding: 100px 24px;
    color: var(--text-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .leading-section::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.04) 0%, transparent 50%);
    animation: sectionGradient 15s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  @keyframes sectionGradient { 0% { transform: translateX(0); } 100% { transform: translateX(10%); } }

  .leading-content { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .leading-content h3 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-color); letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .lead-copy { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto 3rem; }
  .leading-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 20px; text-align: left; }

  .leading-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px 26px;
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), border-color 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s;
    position: relative;
  }
  .leading-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.1);
  }
  .leading-label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--primary-color); display: block; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .leading-headline { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-color); line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .leading-detail { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; }
  .leading-detail a { color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; }
  .leading-detail a:hover { opacity: 0.75; }

  .results-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: rgba(10, 0, 20, 0.8);
    padding: 100px 24px;
    color: var(--text-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .results-content { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .results-content h3 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3.5rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .results-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 32px; }
  .result-item { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .result-number { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary-color); }
  .result-label { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.4; }

  .leadership-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--background-color);
    padding: 100px 24px;
    color: var(--text-color);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .leadership-content { max-width: 980px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .leadership-content h3 { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 3rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }

  .leadership-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 28px; }
  .leadership-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    text-align: left;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    border-radius: 14px;
    transition: border-color 0.4s, box-shadow 0.4s, transform 0.4s;
  }
  .leadership-row:hover { border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3); box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .leadership-when { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; padding-top: 4px; }
  .role-time { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--primary-color); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .role-company { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-color); font-weight: 500; }
  .leadership-what h4 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-color); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .leadership-what p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7; }

  .leadership-cta { margin-top: 2rem; }
  .text-cta { color: var(--primary-color); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .text-cta:hover { opacity: 0.7; }

  .cta-section {
    width: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--background-color) 0%, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.08) 100%);
    padding: 110px 24px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08);
  }
  .cta-content { max-width: 680px; text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .cta-tag { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--primary-color); display: block; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .cta-content h3 { font-size: 2.1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1.2rem; color: var(--text-color); letter-spacing: -0.01em; line-height: 1.25; }
  .cta-content p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 2.2rem; line-height: 1.7; }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.95rem 2.4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a855f7 0%, #7c3aed 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px var(--primary-glow);
  }
  .cta-button:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.5); }
  .cta-button-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.95rem 2.4rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    color: var(--text-color);
    border-radius: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.25);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }
  .cta-button-secondary:hover { background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08); border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.45); transform: translateY(-2px); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .leading-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .results-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
    .leading-content h3, .results-content h3, .leadership-content h3, .cta-content h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .result-number { font-size: 2rem; }
    .leading-section, .results-section, .leadership-section, .cta-section { padding: 70px 16px; }
    .leadership-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 12px; padding: 22px 22px; }
  }
</style>
